page.title: 01Around Christchurch Harbour
page.content:
{MUDEFORD}-Residential,mainly retirement area.Family holiday resort. Sandy beaches.
{STANPIT }-Residential.Nature reserve-marshland-salt and fresh water.Birds,wild plants.Common land grazing.
{CHRISTCHURCH HARBOUR,MUDEFORD QUAY}- Sailing.Sea fishing(seasonal salmon netting,crab,lobster,mackerel).Wind surfing.Avon river with Royalty Fishing and Stour rivers flow in. Archeological site at Hengistbury Head.
{HISTORICAL CHRISTCHURCH}-Priory Church Constable's House.Castle Keep. Red House Museum.
